<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯看了看自己的家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要钱。” 他想，“我可以卖掉一点东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，普斯拿着金币走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯非常惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你从哪里拿到的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯耸耸肩。“国王给我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯挠了挠头。“国王？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯点点头。“我们是朋友。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯把金币给卡拉巴斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，普斯！谢谢！” 卡拉巴斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯笑着点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很快，会有更多好事发生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯每天都去拜访国王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他每天都带去礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“公爵送给您的。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王很喜欢普斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>歌手为普斯唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小丑为普斯表演。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，普斯和国王一起吃午餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟我说说公爵吧。” 国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他善良吗？他帅吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯笑了。“公爵又诚实又善良。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他穿着整洁吗？” 国王问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“非常整洁。” 普斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他很有钱，穿着讲究。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！” 国王说，“我想见见他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“糟了。” 他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可不能带主人来这里。国王会发现他很穷！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯想了想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的主人……嗯……最近很忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是你们一定很快就能见面了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>